
Major components

Satellite Ingest Gateway (edge): receives raw downlink frames (binary), does light validation & framing.

Message Layer (Streaming Bus): durable log — e.g., Apache Kafka / Pulsar — for decoupling.

Raw Object Store: write raw frames/packets to object storage (S3 / MinIO / Ceph) with partitioning.

Metadata Catalog: RDBMS or wide-column store for indexing files, ingestion status, checksums, spatial/temporal indexes.

Processing Cluster: stream processors (Flink / Spark Streaming / Beam) and batch jobs for heavy transforms, tiling, reformatting (GeoTIFF/COG/HDF5), analytics.

Derived Store / OLAP: columnar store or data lake (Parquet/ORC) for analytics; Geo-indexed tile store for imagery.

Serving API / Retrieval: REST/gRPC service for queries, pre-signed URLs, authentication.

Control Plane: Orchestration (Kubernetes), config, autoscale rules.

Monitoring & Alerting: Prometheus + Grafana, distributed tracing, logs.

DR / Geo-replication: cross-region replication for critical data.
